en </div><div class="t m19d9 x5a h4 y1620 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there. Her confidence in Him was un-</div><div class="t m179 x5a h4 y19f0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">broken, but she thought of her dearly loved </div><div class="t m91 x5a h4 ybab ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">brother, whom Jesus also had loved. With </div><div class="t m2dd x5a h4 y1698 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">grief surging in her heart because Christ </div><div class="t m241a x52 h4 y1986 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[29] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
